        <para>Download (HTTP): <ulink url="&gtkhtml-download-http;"/></para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>Download (FTP): <ulink url="&gtkhtml-download-ftp;"/></para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>Download MD5 sum: &gtkhtml-md5sum;</para>
      </listitem>
